{"tid":915563,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IOS 終於可以自製WhatsApp Stickers！","createTime":"2018-11-25T05:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T23:28:46.000Z","uid":223797,"like":12,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7aaf78096894bf3c6dd25bf3a64ee1687db6739a","tid":915563,"uid":223797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟不才，應朋友訴求上星期整左隻 iOS app 幫大家可以自製WhatsApp Sticker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身想等我第二個bug fix version 出到街先同大家講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但PK 蘋果唔批我個新 version ，話咩大多同類型app 又話要依賴其他app 先得咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(DKLM sticker 緊係要WhatsApp 先用到，佢都on99999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n依家個app隨時有機會俾人落架，大家想自製whatsapp sticker就down 左先<br />\n(down 左既app 蘋果落我架都影響唔到你用)<br />\n<br />\nMyStickers:<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mystickers/id1442605866?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fmystickers%2Fid1442605866%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=tKJvl9cJ4JGxj2E%2F8UpRZBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=585fad4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mystickers/id1442605866?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/132720_2d5972534efb4dfcbba906495c6b978b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F132720_2d5972534efb4dfcbba906495c6b978b.png&h=b637351b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/132724_3f0b9dfb950cc07d3d54abc415a9bcb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F132724_3f0b9dfb950cc07d3d54abc415a9bcb7.png&h=0b5b1162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個version 有bug ：<br />\n- 入唔齊name 同 icon 圖會彈app<br />\n- 入太多太大既圖會爆memory 彈app<br />\n- 圖 file size 大過 100KB 會用jpeg 壓縮冇左透明底<br />\n<br />\n祝大家自製到sticker 唔洗俾android fd 屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fddf56aac6354f709b77b0b0378dcd3450da25","tid":915563,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"395e065770a9101b61d3e8b1699525ee551b20fd","tid":915563,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"師兄。細過100 kb都係冇左透明喎"},{"pid":"5217a0b4d810fba4fb66849164aa30c90ef18560","tid":915563,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"唔整 web 版？"},{"pid":"5d7605b52cd3c972433060fa66dd061f65e80581","tid":915563,"uid":190604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef37a41679d2d236e331eea0e491f637f79cc13","tid":915563,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:33:13.000Z","msg":"呢個version 有bug ：<br />\n- 入唔齊name 同 icon 圖會彈app<br />\n- 入太多太大既圖會爆memory 彈app<br />\n- 圖 file size 大過 100KB 會用jpeg 壓縮冇左透明底<br />\n<br />\n咁多限制，不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但正評給樓主。<br />\n<br />\n我依家都係用 Android 整完再 Whatsapp send番去 iPhone<br />\nIOS 套 Picsart 連退地都做唔到。"},{"pid":"ca3d8368b3ab5a9164f88832055e4f9939af8f17","tid":915563,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5217a0b4d810fba4fb66849164aa30c90ef18560","tid":915563,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"唔整 web 版？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"條友真係唔識架喎"},{"pid":"0460fd427d240d8a05b45cb15f376152dfc53dd3","tid":915563,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"push, 正評"},{"pid":"f9be4620f750f3bcd18387765c36ccb6e6fd51e7","tid":915563,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395e065770a9101b61d3e8b1699525ee551b20fd","tid":915563,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"師兄。細過100 kb都係冇左透明喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"same <br />\nios9淨係得呢個app可以import到成套sticker <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8082d800214c076b9218cbe9ec45bf4fe4564a","tid":915563,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9be4620f750f3bcd18387765c36ccb6e6fd51e7","tid":915563,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395e065770a9101b61d3e8b1699525ee551b20fd","tid":915563,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"師兄。細過100 kb都係冇左透明喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"same <br />\nios9淨係得呢個app可以import到成套sticker <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"iOS 9麻煩update啦 之前整ipa果陣都好多iOS9 user話用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fddd660ccc5a51b51130cda5dd7a50b64241f4"